Version 1:

Design something that helps international students who move abroad make friends.

Design something that helps people who struggle with social isolation find others with the same shared interests.

Version 2:

Design an application for people aged 18-30 who move abroad find others with the same interests.

Version 3:

Design an application to help bring people aged 18-30 with the same interests whom have social issues together.

Final Version:

Design a digital substitute where young adults can interact based on shared interests.

